{
  "stem": "27335.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But not-- not-- not-- I thought there was an incident.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She gave me a Hungarian map.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the name, you know when you get it, these kind of things that carry it with you on-- on the-- causes and so on, you would write Raymond.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when they captured me, they found that name, Raymond.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think that was the reason-- that was the reason they found that name.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it didn't take them very much to trace Mrs.-- Mrs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] though.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I thought it was some kind of a betrayal or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But-- but no, [NON-ENGLISH] had-- had nothing to do with-- with that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But anyway, that was a month later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then on my-- on my research, and all that, I met people who were-- especially the one who was a prisoner himself, a young boy, who was about the same age as Hannah, but they-- they-- they used him as a-- as a cleaner.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Swept the cleaning in the-- in the-- in the prison.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was able to contact him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, when I squeezed him, he-- he remembered something that he saw, this [NON-ENGLISH] around Hannah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Somewhere on the-- on the-- on the corridors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because then how her-- her mother was-- was arrested.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so-- and then what I was able to put together, the poor girl who walked into his trap because first by the side, he knew that-- she knew that he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was at party-- he was in the Partisan during the Partisan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I can proceed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He must be a comrade, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this put together, he probably ask her where are you from?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Budapest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He probably did 18-- 18 [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
